# COMPILE with Eclipse
############################################################################
# If you have any problems, configure Eclipse to automatically 
# rebuild your project when editing native code
#
# ... and set Target to "Manual" under Project->Properties->Run/Debug Settings
# Launch configurations for "..."
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Click on Run or Ctrl+F11 :)
